summary:
Same thing as this mod except I removed all the cell edits so that the zombies only appear in the leveled lists. Should make the mod more stable and compatible with other mods.

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56379/?

Let me know if there are any problems.

Same thing as this mod except I removed all the cell edits so that the zombies only appear in the leveled lists. Should make the mod more stable and compatible with other mods.

Let me know if there are any problems.

Includes "nude" version, some zombies have weapons some don't. If there is enough interest I might convert the other non-nude and no weapon versions etc.
